    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>For more details about the demo, please refer to the demo page.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177800/extras/d384339b96d41eb3010955887948e952.poster.avif?t=1770967053\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177800/extras/d384339b96d41eb3010955887948e952.webm?t=1770967053\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177800/extras/d384339b96d41eb3010955887948e952.mp4?t=1770967053\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>“The best way to clean? Kill the mess at its source.”</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A cleaner, commissioned by the Kim Demon before her vacation, sucks up everything that gets in the way of cleaning in this <strong>2D pixel roguelite shooting</strong> game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177800/extras/6ba3d2e6b21848ef1cb03a172b1093df.poster.avif?t=1770967053\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177800/extras/6ba3d2e6b21848ef1cb03a172b1093df.webm?t=1770967053\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177800/extras/6ba3d2e6b21848ef1cb03a172b1093df.mp4?t=1770967053\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A… dungeon…?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don’t worry! Dungeons aren’t scary lairs anymore.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >They’re fully licensed businesses, operating legally under proper regulations!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Dungeon Cleaning…?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once upon a time, there was Kim Demon, weary from endless work.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Alas! The dungeon’s seasonal inspection had fallen on the very same days as her seaside holiday with her fellow villains.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a fluster, she rummaged through her chamber… and there it was : <strong>A</strong> <strong>leaflet for a cleaning service.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And so the question remains—will everything turn out all right?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177800/extras/71f728730eb149a50200b1b516dd9b6d.poster.avif?t=1770967053\" width=1170 height=494 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177800/extras/71f728730eb149a50200b1b516dd9b6d.webm?t=1770967053\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177800/extras/71f728730eb149a50200b1b516dd9b6d.mp4?t=1770967053\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Mighty Vacuum!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The cleaner’s most trusted companion is none other than <strong><i>“B.F.V (Best Friend Vacuum)”</i></strong>.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Small objects and enemy projectiles can be <strong>sucked up and turned into ammo</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bigger objects</strong> may clog the vacuum head, but can still be <strong>launched back out</strong>.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The B.F.V isn’t just a cleaning tool — it’s a <i>shield, a weapon, a tool, and a strategy all in one</i>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><u>(But beware: not everything can be absorbed.)</u></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177800/extras/b58f7d19ae38d98e5f2264283d3b6fa9.poster.avif?t=1770967053\" width=1170 height=494 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177800/extras/b58f7d19ae38d98e5f2264283d3b6fa9.webm?t=1770967053\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177800/extras/b58f7d19ae38d98e5f2264283d3b6fa9.mp4?t=1770967053\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Don’t be fooled by the cute(pixel)look!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >They’re all just filthy things waiting for you to clean up!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sure, the process will be a <strong>chaotic mess</strong>…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But as long as it’s clean in the end, isn’t that what matters?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177800/extras/45cf52be021e3b5aaa9354f27263e7b8.poster.avif?t=1770967053\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177800/extras/45cf52be021e3b5aaa9354f27263e7b8.webm?t=1770967053\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177800/extras/45cf52be021e3b5aaa9354f27263e7b8.mp4?t=1770967053\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>In this world nothing can be said to be certain, except death and taxes, cleaning.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Yes—quite literally.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each time you fall, the dungeon reshapes itself, offering a new run, a new challenge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Here, death isn’t the end… it’s the start of another round of cleaning.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Is It Wrong to Try to Pick Up Strangers(or NPCs) in a Dungeon?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Not everything in the dungeon is out to get in your way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sometimes, you’ll meet those who lend a hand with your cleaning!</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some NPCs, once rescued, will move into the lobby, <strong>offering stat boosts or starting funcs</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Others appear as one-off events, <strong>giving you unexpected aid</strong> in a tight spot.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But whether that hand is <strong>a lifeline… or a landmine, you’ll only find out by taking it</strong>.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>No Two Cleaners Clean Alike.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The dungeon is full of weapons and vacuum upgrades waiting to be discovered.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From <strong>melee, pistols, rifles, snipers, shotguns, and explosives</strong>— </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >to everything from simple stat boosts to wild, <strong>unexpected special effects</strong>…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find your own unique way to clean!</p>",
